  "prompt": "What are the signs that a Taurus man really likes you?",
  "response": "A Taurus man is typically known for his loyalty, practicality, and patience, which can manifest in specific behaviors when he is interested in someone romantically. Here are some signs that a Taurus man really likes you:\n\n1. **Consistent Attention and Effort**: He will consistently make time for you, engage in deep conversations, and be reliable in communicating.\n\n2. **Physical Affection**: Taurus men are tactile and appreciate physical closeness. If he seeks opportunities for physical touch, like holding your hand, hugging, or sitting close to you, it's a sign he likes you.\n\n3. **Generosity**: He will likely spoil you with gifts, thoughtful gestures, and acts of service. This stems from his desire to care for and nurture those he loves.\n\n4. **Interest in Your Life**: He will show genuine curiosity about your interests, hobbies, and goals, and will remember small details about things you\u2019ve shared.\n\n5. **Protectiveness**: Taurus men are protective by nature. If he shows concern for your wellbeing and goes out of his way to ensure you're safe and comfortable, he likely cares deeply for you.\n\n6. **Quality Time**: He values spending meaningful time with you, whether it's going on dates, sharing meals, or simply enjoying cozy nights together.\n\n7. **Slow and Steady Pace**: Taurus men are not known for rushing into relationships. If he is taking his time to build a solid foundation with you, it means he sees long-term potential.\n\n8. **Sharing Personal Things**: He will invite you into his personal space, share his interests and passions, and may open up about his feelings and thoughts.\n\nThese behaviors are typical of a Taurus man when he is genuinely interested in someone. Keep in mind that everyone's personality is unique, so while these signs are common, individual differences can also play a significant role.",
